    key: "privacy_modal_two_content_sub_text_two",
    en: "Zuri is committed to ensuring our infrastructure is secure, redundant, and reliable, while providing your team with tools to administer your environment. We are proud to exceed the industry standard when it comes to protecting your organization and we've outlined many of our security practices and certifications on our website.",
